**同年簽約女子網球選手[[崔西·奧斯丁|崔西·奧斯丁]]，她後來成為當年同時獲得温布尔登网球锦标赛與美國網球公開賽最年輕冠軍。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sneakerfiles.com/pony-sneakers/pony-tracy-austin/ |title=Pony Tracy Austin |access-date=2011-10-18 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028080753/https://www.sneakerfiles.com/pony-sneakers/pony-tracy-austin/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
