**4月，簽下北美足球聯盟的最高得分的頭號球員[[乔治·基纳利亚|乔治·基纳利亚]]。
**8月，Carlos Monzon 穿著PONY登上運動畫刊封面。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web |url=http://boxrec.com/media/index.php/Sports_Illustrated_Magazine_Covers:_1970s |title=Sports Illustrated Magazine Covers: 1970s |access-date=2011-10-28 |archive-date=2019-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607214851/http://boxrec.com/media/index.php/Sports_Illustrated_Magazine_Covers:_1970s |dead-url=no }}</ref>

